# Full-Cycle E2E Test Environment Variables
#
# These tests connect to the REAL Courier API (production).
# You must set COURIER_AUTH_TOKEN to a valid API key for your workspace.
#
# To get your API key: app.courier.com → Settings → API Keys
#
# To run: pnpm --filter @trycourier/react-designer test:e2e:fullcycle
#
# ─── Required ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Courier REST API auth token (workspace API key, NOT the JWT)
COURIER_AUTH_TOKEN=""

# ─── Designer Config ─────────────────────────────────────────
# These are used by the dev server (apps/editor-dev) to connect to the GraphQL API.
# Copy from apps/editor-dev/.env or set your own.
VITE_API_URL="https://api.courier.com/client/q"
VITE_TEMPLATE_ID="template-id"
VITE_TENANT_ID="tenant-id"
VITE_JWT_TOKEN=""
